; Coverage test for filters.cc changed_value_posts with --gain
; Tests the revaluation output path in output_intermediate_prices.
; When market prices change between posts, revaluations are generated.
; This exercises the AMOUNT type case when the
; last_total is a simple amount.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/02/01 AAPL $160.00
P 2024/03/01 AAPL $155.00

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Stock    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash    $-1500.00

test reg --gain Assets:Stock
24-Feb-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                  $100.00      $100.00
24-Mar-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                  $-50.00       $50.00
end test
